Package: gdt
Architecture: all
Depends: python3 (>= 3.6), ${misc:Depends}
Description: Per-directory color themes for the Ghostty terminal
 gdt manages per-directory color themes for the Ghostty terminal.
 When you cd into a mapped directory, your terminal colors change
 automatically via OSC escape sequences and a zsh chpwd hook.
